{"tha-ap345:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap345:0.2":"Ekapadumiyavagga ","tha-ap345:0.3":"Dhajadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap345:1.1":"“Tisso nama ahu sattha, ","tha-ap345:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap345:1.3":"Tayopadhikkhaye disva, ","tha-ap345:1.4":"dhajam aropitam maya. ","tha-ap345:2.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap345:2.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap345:2.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap345:2.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap345:3.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap345:3.2":"devarajjam akarayim; ","tha-ap345:3.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap345:3.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap345:4.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap345:4.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap345:4.3":"Anubhomi sakam kammam, ","tha-ap345:4.4":"pubbe sukatamattano. ","tha-ap345:5.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap345:5.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap345:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap345:5.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap345:6.1":"Icchamano caham ajja, ","tha-ap345:6.2":"sakananam sapabbatam; ","tha-ap345:6.3":"Khomadussena chadeyyam, ","tha-ap345:6.4":"tada mayham kate phalam. ","tha-ap345:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap345:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap345:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap345:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhajadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap345:9.1":"Dhajadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}